%N A395256 Number of transitive relations that are not posets.
%C A395256 a(n) counts the transitive relations on n labeled elements that fail to be partial orders (i.e., that violate reflexivity and/or antisymmetry).
%F A395256 a(n) = A006905(n) - A001035(n).
%e A395256 a(1)=1 because the only transitive relations on the 1-set X={1} is the null relation.
%Y A395256 Cf. A006905, A001035.
